Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:37.11,Phone,Sign 0137,0000,0000,0000,,8:50 PM \NMay 7 (Sunday)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:49.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:51.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.72,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:57.63,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Only Aeroflot has kept me \Nwaiting as long as you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:01.14,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Japanese dogeza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:06.64,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor will be staying in \NHasetsu to be my coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:11.70,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, it's surreal, more like \Nhaving a god around than a coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:10.40,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Resting is a part of work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:17.57,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,To think that a coach of my very own \Nis going to be here every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.24,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And that coach is Victor Nikiforov himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.20,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He said I could pay his coaching fees later,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.27,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I wonder how expensive it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:32.21,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you tend to flub your jumps \Nwhen something is on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:37.80,Title,Sign 0234,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Fourth Skate \N{\fs20}Like Yourself... \NAnd Complete the Free Program!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:37.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Like Yourself... And Complete the Free Program!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.30,Yutopia,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu Hot Springs \NYu-topia Katsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:44.05,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, maybe we should nix having \Nthree quads in your free program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:44.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I-If I want to win the Grand \NPrix Final, I need those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:49.66,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.31,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there's only one quad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.57,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,just get a perfect score on \Nthe program components!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:59.45,SignA,Sign 0256,0000,0000,0000,,Figure Skating {\c&H1853F9&}Scoring System
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:03:00.03,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let me pause here to explain the \Nscoring system in figure skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:02.01,Technical,Sign 0301,0000,0000,0000,,Technical Elements Score (TES)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.54,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Jumps and spins count \Ntoward a technical score.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.51,Components,Sign 0303,0000,0000,0000,,Program Components Score (PCS)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:05.94,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Choreography and interpretation count \Ntoward a presentation score.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:09.83,Technical,Sign 0307,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFC58A&}TES {\c&HAA171E&}+ {\c&HECC5F3&}PCS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.83,Deductions,Sign 0307,0000,0000,0000,,Deductions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:09.83,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The total score is a sum of those \Ntwo, minus any deductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:09.83,Total,Sign 0307,0000,0000,0000,,Total Score
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:14.41,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When I skate, I tend to lose technical \Npoints by missing jumps,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:18.83,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but close the gap through \Nthe presentation score.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:22.38,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, this isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.84,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:27.60,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, do you know why I decided \Nto become your coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:32.21,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I was drawn to you because of the music...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.88,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,The way you skate like your \Nbody is creating music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:38.61,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I want to create a high-difficulty \Nprogram to maximize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.36,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Only I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.11,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,That's the gut feeling I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.32,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,And the short program validated it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:50.03,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you should produce \Nyour next free program.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:50.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But my coach has always chosen my music—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.26,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more fun to do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But my previous coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.84,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Who was your coach again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.02,Default,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:05.84,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.29,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao, ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.04,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you since the Grand Prix Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.11,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Victor's your coach now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:15.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.41,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.23,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao, ciao, Celestino!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:20.99,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his coach, Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.78,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing at being a coach in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.36,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:26.91,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.24,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you let Yuri \Nchoose his program music?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.17,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:32.57,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,I usually select music for my skaters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.00,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,but I also let them choose if they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.22,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri only brought me a piece once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.50,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it was composed by an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.51,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't bad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.82,Default - flashback,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can win with this music?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.26,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:49.39,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please choose the music for me after all, Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:53.32,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri never had confidence in himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:57.15,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,I told him time and again \Nto trust himself more, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.21,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Celestino...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:05.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to redeem myself at \Nthe next Grand Prix Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:11.59,Default,Ce,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted to hear you say \Nat last year's Grand Prix Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bring myself to \Ncontact him for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.17,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.02,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Could I hear this music he mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:21.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.10,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.78,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your coach, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.18,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.93,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,That little piggy's producing \Nhis own free program?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.56,Default - italics,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,How are you, Yuri-kun in Russia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.18,Default - italics,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you choose your free program?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.59,Default - italics,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:42.03,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yuko trying to scout the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:42.82,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.17,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,But producing his own program, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.14,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.73,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, did you go to Japan to find a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:51.74,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,No. Get off me, Mila.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:55.11,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Are you horny because you \Ndumped that hockey player?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:56.87,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't put myself in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.63,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get myself almost killed just \Nfor going on a date with another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.60,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,I've been practicing lifts lately, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.88,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down, hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.63,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only three years older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.26,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri. Mila.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.68,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,Coach Yakov...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Put me down already! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.13,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two switching to pairs skating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.39,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.15,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to Yuri in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.67,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,He used to hate practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.02,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,He was arrogant about his abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.91,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,because no one in his age group rivaled him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:34.04,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,But I think his face-off with Yuri Katsuki \Nin Japan was his wake-up call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:37.03,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,This may make things interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.27,Default,Moms,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:39.92,Default,Moms,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.50,Default,Moms,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lilia Baranovskaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.80,Default,Moms,0000,0000,0000,,The former prima ballerina \Nof the Bolshoi Ballet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.68,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Lilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.17,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,So which one is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.48,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't like what I see, I'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.18,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.31,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,No cavities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.64,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.64,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Physically, he's abysmal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.69,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,We start from square one with ballet lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.81,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.92,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.82,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,I will choreograph your free program.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.82,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,First, I've decided on your next goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:13.07,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Become this season's principal—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:16.20,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,no, prima ballerina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:19.46,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,If you are willing to sell your soul to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.27,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,P-Prima ballerina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.55,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,If selling my soul is all it takes to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.84,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my whole body, no holds barred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.34,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lilia Baranovskaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:36.29,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Go home and pack up your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.85,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be living with me from now on to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.85,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,With Yakov, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.06,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Lilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.77,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong, Yakov.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.62,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to get back together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.55,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:49.11,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,I... I wasn't hoping for that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.29,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:54.09,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,but Yurio-kun's coach brought in his ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:56.50,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's getting scolded by her day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.62,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Have you chosen the music for \Nyour free program, Yuri-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I had Victor listen to one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.71,Default - flashback,V,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. So this is how it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But his reaction was lukewarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:09.00,SFX,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Smackdown
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:09.00,Default - flashback,V,0000,0000,0000,,You should think of other possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:15.72,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,My usual way was to have my coach pick \Nsomething from what was available,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.76,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and to let him choreograph it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.78,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But Victor wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:26.36,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He choreographed his own programs and \Nhad new music written to create stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:31.18,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I did dream about doing that\Nmyself someday, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Phichit-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He's practicing back home in Thailand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Phichit-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sawasdee krab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.15,Default,Phichit,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.09,Default,Phichit,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while. How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:57.59,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You're practicing back in Thailand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:09:01.48,Default,Phichit,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Detroit's boring now that you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.57,Default,Phichit,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you should come visit Bangkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.11,Default,Phichit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:06.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Khob khun, kup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:12.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Phichit-kun, do you remember \Nhow I had a music demo made?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.13,Default,Pichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:14.77,Default,Pichi,0000,0000,0000,,By the conservatory student?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.95,Default,Pichi,0000,0000,0000,,You asked her to compose it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It got shelved in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.17,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, and after you spent time composing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:24.87,Default - flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine. Just keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:26.67,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.78,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Things got awkward with her after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.21,Default,Pichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.84,Default,Pichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put out feelers to see where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.74,Default,Pichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's not mad or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.10,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This piece has been bothering me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.64,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a bit weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.60,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:52.48,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her to compose a piece that'd \Nexpress my whole career as a skater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.56,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She did capture it pretty well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.99,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,My underwhelming life in \Ncompetitive figure skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.49,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What should I have done differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.06,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:09.22,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.83,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Throw yourself away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.98,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Your past self is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.12,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,People who can be reborn as many times \Nas necessary are the strong ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.34,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Victor!\N{\fs17}Welcome Back, Katsuki Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.34,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,What? You still haven't chosen the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:24.23,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you trust your own decisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.48,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Just try to remember something, \Nlike when a girlfriend loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Sorry! Right now, it's just that I—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.69,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. You've never had a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.88,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, let's go somewhere today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:42.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.61,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, let's go take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:45.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.95,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, let's go to sleep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this guilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.27,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.97,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.81,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, seagulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:15.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Black-tailed gulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.09,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:22.91,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reminded of St. Petersburg when \NI hear seagulls in the early morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:26.82,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd leave that city,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:29.80,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,so I never used to notice the seagulls' cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.06,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ever have times like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:38.98,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,There was a girl in Detroit who was really \Npushy and kept talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:42.30,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,One time, a rink mate got into an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.47,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty torn up with worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.28,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the hospital waiting \Nroom with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.12,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,When she hugged me to comfort me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.81,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I shoved her away without thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.96,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:59.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want her to think \NI was feeling unsettled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:04.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like she was intruding on my \Nfeelings or something, and I hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:11.53,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But then I realized that Minako-sensei, \NNishigori, Yuko-chan, and my family
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,never treated me like a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They all had faith that I'd \Nkeep growing as a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and they never stepped over the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.73,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you're not weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.58,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,No one else thinks that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.60,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to be to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.96,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,A father figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:35.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.78,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,A brother, then? A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:41.04,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Then, your boyfriend, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.09,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I can try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:42.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:46.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay who you are, Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've always looked up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I ignored you because I didn't want \Nyou to see my shortcomings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it up to you with my skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.71,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I won't let you off easy, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.71,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,That's my way of showing my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:12.39,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When I open up, he meets me where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.24,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be afraid to open up more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to redo the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.12,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Until she's done, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:37.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me all the jumps \Nthat you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.10,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:56.52,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Even the king crab we ate yesterday \Nhad a better free leg than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.18,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Do it again, starting from the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.30,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Your response?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.12,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:05.40,Default - italics,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been good that \Nhe left Victor's side early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:10.16,Default - italics,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to rebuild his strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.03,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Victor!\N{\fs17}Welcome Back, Katsuki Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor, please let me do that one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.04,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Hasn't it been tens \Nof thousands of times?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Just thirteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:22.45,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought this for a while, \Nbut you have pretty good stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have that, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:28.93,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,You said you get hungry when you're \Nnervous in competition, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:32.39,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't suffered any major injuries, \Nand you're younger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:37.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.98,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Is it getting that thin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no! Everything's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:45.38,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hurt... I can't recover from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:51.07,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, those two seem to get along fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:14:59.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The music for the free program's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.18,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,If you want more impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.43,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,maybe the last jump can \Nbe a quadruple toe loop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.94,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,With your stamina, I think you can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.85,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,You'd rather not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.65,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.30,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.15,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, did you change the musical theme?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.91,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:39.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The theme is "on my love."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.92,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.88,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.32,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.05,sign_24855_439_Snack_Bar___Kach,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Kachu\NSnack Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.65,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:15.66,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Prix assignments were announced?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.12,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, crap, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.88,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you three realize what time it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.15,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! The assignments!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:21.91,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.12,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.13,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,The assignments are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.22,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:30.55,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd the little Japanese \Npiggy get assigned?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.45,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:35.51,Congrats,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats on Your Assignment in the GP Series, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.06,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll explain which events \Nyou'll be competing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.40,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,But first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.74,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Katsuki family still doesn't \Nknow much about figure skating,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.72,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,we'll give a simple explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.17,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that'd be very helpful.
