Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.57,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,What is the Figure Skating Grand Prix series?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:54.91,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Skaters with high scores in the previous year
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:52.46,Map,Sign 1652,0000,0000,0000,,Czech Republic  Russia  China  South Korea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.46,Map,Sign 1653,0000,0000,0000,,Czech Republic  Russia  China  South Korea \NSwitzerland  Italy  Russia  Thailand  USA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.13,Map,Sign 1654,0000,0000,0000,,Czech Republic  Russia  China  South Korea \NSwitzerland  Italy  Russia  Thailand  USA \NKazakhstan  Canada
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.84,Map,Sign 1655,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1201BB&\fs20}First Event: Skate America
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:59.46,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,participate in a maximum of two \Ncompetitions out of six worldwide.
