Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.59,Map,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H19B567&\fs20}Third Event: Cup of China
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:16:59.97,Map,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB564D8&\fs20}Fourth Event: NHK Trophy (Japan)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.58,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Only the top six skaters advance \Nto the Grand Prix Final,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.35,Map,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H88366F&\fs20}Fifth Event: Trophée de France
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.58,Map,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H048343&\fs20}Sixth Event: Rostelecom Cup (Russia)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.29,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,which decides who's number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.29,Map,Sign 1704,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H03C3C1&\fs20}Top 6 Male Figure Skaters
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:08.10,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,And this season, Yuri's been assigned to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:13.05,Map,Sign 1709,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEE1500&\fs20}Third Event: Cup of China!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.97,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,the third event, the Cup of China!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:13.05,Phichit,,0000,0000,0000,,Phichit Chulanont
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:13.05,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri's former rink mate, Phichit \Nfrom Thailand, will be there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Phichit-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.64,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,And his second event will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:22.81,Map,Sign 1719,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB564D8&\fs20}Sixth Event: Rostelecom Cup (Russia)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.53,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,The sixth event, Russia's Rostelecom Cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:22.81,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be up against his fated rival, Yuri Plisetsky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.81,Map,Sign 1721,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}I'll kill you! \N\N{\c&H38CA7E&\fs22}Yuri Plisetsky
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.29,Yurio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,200)}Yurio
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.67,Default,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wow, Yurio! Davai, davai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.87,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm already facing Yurio \Nin the Rostelecom Cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:31.08,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be minding the house \Nduring the season, Maccachin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.07,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:36.57,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be my first time in a Grand Prix \Nseries without Victor in the lineup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:39.14,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet if you show up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.98,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,with Victor as your coach, they'll think \Nyou stole him from the sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.96,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe skating fans worldwide hate you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.18,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! We're on your side, Yuri-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:50.96,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.34,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come cheer you on this season, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:58.22,Map,Sign 1753,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7146BA&\fs22}Yuri!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.48,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,First up is the Cup of China!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.04,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.21,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.22,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,In the Nationals...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I think I finished eleventh because \NI messed up my prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.35,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So you have to compete \Nin the block championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.57,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're talking about domestic competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:13.98,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,To explain, Yuri-kun had a big-time \Nloss in last year's Nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.94,Board,Sign 1811,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese National Championships!! \NUtter Defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.00,Board,Sign 1814,0000,0000,0000,,Qualification Loss
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:18.27,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,So this year, he has to work his way \Nup from qualifying competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:19.38,Board,Sign 1817,0000,0000,0000,,Must Compete in Qualifying Competitions
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:20.13,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,So his first event this season is the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:22.62,Board,Sign 1821,0000,0000,0000,,Chugoku, Shikoku, and Kyushu Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.62,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Chugoku, Shikoku, and Kyushu \NChampionship in September.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.45,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be his comeback competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.32,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.41,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll breeze through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:29.24,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Minami-kun from Fukuoka \Nwill be competing in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.69,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he beat Yuri in the Nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:36.06,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Minami Kenjiro from Kyushu, said to be \Nthe #1 star among younger skaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:38.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:43.35,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been more than six months since \NDecember, when I thought I was done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.51,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.10,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,We can cheer you on this year, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.85,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.52,Default,YDad,0000,0000,0000,,We need to use this chance to make money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.07,Default,YMom,0000,0000,0000,,You'll autograph a sign, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:19:00.11,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I thought I was \Nfighting all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.93,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But now that Victor's here, \Nthat's totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.53,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Some things are still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.62,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Some have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.50,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Now everything feels so new.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.89,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I may never be able to regain what I've lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:21.39,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I can clearly see what's \Nin front of me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.33,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.30,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.86,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.05,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,He was so reluctant at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.96,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,but he's becoming more and \Nmore like a prima ballerina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:12.52,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I only have a short window \Nbefore my body changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:17.65,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take advantage of \Neverything I can right now to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.72,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Figure skaters are only competitive \Nfor a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.56,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This will probably be my last \Ncompetitive figure skating season.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:05.08,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long Victor will stick around
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.38,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,or how long my body will hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.71,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So please, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:14.75,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Give me Victor's time, if only just for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:18.96,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you haven't named the \Npiece. What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:27.09,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:29.66,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,September...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:34.09,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor's and my season will finally begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:37.02,Map,Sign 2135,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Send the Power of Sports Throughout Japan! \NChugoku, Shikoku, and Kyushu Figure Skating Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.02,TBC,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:12.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first official competition in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:13.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:14.66,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,This is my coaching debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:16.11,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, what would you like me to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.11,0:23:17.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just your usual clothes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Fifth Skate: Face Beet-Red!! \NIt's the First Competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:26.00,Title,Sign 2321,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Fifth Skate \N{\fs20}Face Beet-Red!! It's the First Competition! \NThe Chugoku, Shikoku, and Kyushu Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:22.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Chugoku, Shikoku, and Kyushu Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:24.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Stay tuned!
